---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | DishBloom">
  <Navbar />
  <article class="legal-page container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 28, 2026</p>
    <p>DishBloom ("we", "us") operates thedishbloom.com. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our service.</p>
    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly: email address, display name, and any content you submit (recipes, photos, reviews). We also collect usage data automatically: pages visited, time spent, device type, and referral source.</p>
    <h2>How we use your information</h2>
    <p>We use your data to provide and improve the service, personalize your experience, send communications you have opted into, and display relevant advertising through our ad partners.</p>
    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>We use third-party advertising companies (such as Ezoic and Google AdSense) to serve ads. These companies may use cookies and similar technologies to serve ads based on your browsing activity.</p>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to maintain your session, remember preferences, and analyze traffic. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at hello@thedishbloom.com.</p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
.legal-page { max-width: 700px; padding: 48px 20px 80px; }
.legal-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.legal-page h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.legal-page p { color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.updated { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-lighter); margin-bottom: 24px; }
</style>
